name: Partner
description: Represents a partner, such as a distributor or reseller.
summary: The {Partner} object in the Salesforce application is used to track relationships between different accounts in the system. It has attributes such as Id, OpportunityId, AccountFromId, AccountToId, Role, IsPrimary, CreatedDate, CreatedById, LastModifiedDate, LastModifiedById, SystemModstamp, IsDeleted, and ReversePartnerId. These attributes store information about the partner relationship, including the role of the partner, creation and modification dates, and whether the partner record has been deleted.
label: Partner
